Years later TK-MIA becomes the shop's institutional memory.

The most important thing isn't the AI.

It's that when Joe retires after 25 years, all the knowledge in Joe's head stays in the system.

That's where I think TK-MIA becomes genuinely valuable for ThyssenKrupp.
